	  loading the menu.
	* configure.ac, terminal/Makefile.am, terminal/terminal-dbus.c: Fix
	  further issues concerning D-BUS 0.31. Remove the runtime library
	  detection, since the SONAME was bumped for D-BUS 0.31.

